Package: omicbot
Title: Data AI Agent Specialized in Omics Data Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Jian", "Wu", email = "wujian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Omicbot provides a lightweight R interface for interactive LLM use in RStudio,
  with guided provider/model setup, secure API-key handling, and quick chat
  workflows. It initializes agents for multiple providers (OpenAI, Google,
  DeepSeek, Alibaba Qwen via OpenAI-compatible, Xiaomi MiMo, and Ollama),
  supports fast console chat, an addin-based quickchat workflow, resumable saved
  chat sessions, and a browser chat launcher. It also includes example omics
  data and violin plot scripts for exploratory visualization workflows.
  Configuration is stored under the RStudio user config directory and can be
  reset or updated interactively.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
